# BwnX Platform - Cursor AI Configuration

## Project Overview
BwnX Platform is a Deep Ocean Recommendations system for Life, Money & Lifestyle.
Built with React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Supabase, and AI integration.

## Development Guidelines

### Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React 19, Vite, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL), AI Integration (OpenAI)
- **Deployment**: GitHub Pages, Auto Deploy via GitHub Actions
- **AI**: OpenAI GPT-3.5/4 for recommendations and search enhancement

### Code Style
- Use TypeScript when possible
- Follow React best practices
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Implement responsive design (mobile-first)
- Use semantic HTML
- Follow accessibility guidelines

### File Structure
```
src/
├── components/          # Reusable UI components
├── lib/                # Utilities and configurations
│   ├── supabase.js     # Database functions
│   ├── ai.js           # AI integration
│   └── utils.js        # Helper functions
├── assets/             # Static assets
├── App.jsx             # Main application
└── main.jsx           # Entry point
```

### Database Schema (Supabase)
```sql
-- Recommendations table
CREATE TABLE recommendations (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  title TEXT NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  category TEXT NOT NULL,
  url TEXT,
  rating DECIMAL(2,1) DEFAULT 0,
  tags TEXT[],
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW(),
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Categories table
CREATE TABLE categories (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  name TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  description TEXT,
  icon TEXT,
  color TEXT,
  count INTEGER DEFAULT 0
);

-- Users table (for future authentication)
CREATE TABLE users (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  email TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
  name TEXT,
  preferences JSONB,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Stats table
CREATE TABLE stats (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  total_recommendations INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  languages_supported INTEGER DEFAULT 10,
  categories INTEGER DEFAULT 8,
  daily_updates TEXT DEFAULT '24/7',
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

